sequenceDiagram
    participant S as KBMS.Server
    participant RN as ReteNetwork
    participant AN as AlphaNode
    participant BN as BetaNode
    participant AG as AgendaManager

    S->>RN: Assert Fact (Ground Truth)
    RN->>AN: Propagate Token (Filtering)
    
    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
        Note right of AN: Incremental Propagation
        AN->>BN: Pass Token (Join Operations)
        BN->>BN: Condition Matching (Memories)
        BN->>AG: Activate Terminal (Fired Rule)
    end
    
    loop Rule Execution
        AG->>AG: Pop Activation (Priority)
        AG->>RN: Assert New Fact
        RN-->>AN: Sub-propagation
    end
    
    RN-->>S: Return ReasoningResult (Fixed-point Closure)
